==Sports==
The sports competed at the 2005 Women's Islamic Games were: [[Track and field athletics|athletics]], [[badminton]], [[basketball]], [[fencing]], [[futsal]], [[golf]], [[gymnastics]], [[Team handball|handball]], [[judo]], [[karate]], [[Squash (sport)|squash]], [[Swimming (sport)|swimming]], [[table tennis]], [[taekwondo]], [[tennis]], and [[volleyball]].
