'''Donbass Equicentre'''  is an equestrian sports centre situated in [[Donetsk]], [[Ukraine]]. The complex was built in [[2009 in Ukraine|2009]] and since then national and international [[show jumping]] tournaments called [[Donbass Tour]] have been held there  annually.

