'''John Ruuka''' (born 13 August 1995) is an [[Kiribati|I-Kiribati]] [[sprint (running)|sprinter]]. He competed at the [[2016 Summer Olympics]] in the [[Athletics at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Men's 100 metres|men's 100 metres]] race; his time of 11.65 seconds in the preliminary round did not qualify him for the first round.<ref>{{cite web|title=John Ruuka |url=https://www.rio2016.com/en/athlete/john-ruka |website=Rio 2016 |accessdate=August 22, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816104806/https://www.rio2016.com/en/athlete/john-ruka |archivedate=August 16, 2016 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Men's 100m - Standings |url=https://www.rio2016.com/en/athletics-standings-at-mens-100m |website=Rio 2016 |accessdate=August 22, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822033050/https://www.rio2016.com/en/athletics-standings-at-mens-100m |archivedate=August 22, 2016 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>

