{{Infobox stadium | name = Tomorr Sinani Sports Palace | nickname = Pallati I Sportit Tomorr Sinani | logo_image = | logo_caption = | image = | caption = | fullname = | former_names = | location = [[Elbasan]], [[Albania]] | coordinates = | broke_ground = | built = | opened = 1982 | renovated = | expanded = | closed = | demolished = | owner = [[Elbasan|Municipality of Elbasan]] | operator = Municipality of Elbasan | surface = | scoreboard = | cost = | architect = | project_manager = | structural engineer = | services engineer = | general_contractor = | main_contractors = | capacity = 2,200 | suites = | record_attendance = | dimensions = | Gross Area = | tenants = BC Elbasani, KV Elbasani | embedded = | website = }}
'''Tomorr Sinani Sports Palace''' is a multi-use sports arena in [[Elbasan]], [[Albania]]. It is owned and operated by the [[Elbasan|Municipality of Elbasan]] and it is the home of the multidisciplinary [[KS Elbasani]].<ref>[https://www.ata.gov.al/elbasan-sheshi-para-pallatit-te-sportit-do-te-kthehet-ne-lulishte/ Elbasan-Sheshi para pallatit të sportit do të kthehet në lulishte]</ref><ref>[http://www.fiba.com/temp/_pdf/FIBAMediaGuide/232.pdf FIBA: Albanian Basketball Federation]</ref><ref>[http://telesport.al/europiani-i-basketbollit-nuk-kemi-pallat-sporti-ku-te-luajme/ Europiani i basketbollit, nuk kemi pallat sporti ku të luajmë]</ref>
